OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781628468
OL,3,CWelsh Government sets out guidance to
OL,4,Ccurb mobile phones in schools
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has issued new
OL,7,Fguidance to reduce pupils' use of
OL,8,Fmobile phones in schools.
OL,10,FEducation Minister Anna Brychan MS
OL,11,Fsays she would "strongly encourage"
OL,12,Fheadteachers to restrict mobile phones
OL,13,Fduring the school day, "up to and
OL,14,Fincluding a full restriction across
OL,15,Fthe school site".
OL,17,FThis follows shortly after the UK
OL,18,FGovernment announced a social media
OL,19,Fban for under 16s.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
