OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781628468
OL,3,CWelsh Government sets out guidance to
OL,4,Ccurb mobile phones in schools
OL,6,FIn a survey conducted by the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment, it found 82% of
OL,8,Frespondents were in favour of
OL,9,Frestrictions on the devices in
OL,10,Feducational settings.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, Education
OL,13,FMinister Anna Brychan MS said: "I want
OL,14,Fheadteachers and governing bodies to
OL,15,Fknow that if they want to institute
OL,16,Fthat complete ban we would support
OL,17,Fthem to do so".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
