OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781628468
OL,3,CWelsh Government sets out guidance to
OL,4,Ccurb mobile phones in schools
OL,6,FSchools will have some discretion in
OL,7,Fhow they apply their policies, with
OL,8,Fthe Education Minister saying she is
OL,9,F"mindful some children will always
OL,10,Fneed exceptions for medical reasons".
OL,12,FThe Children's Commissioner for Wales
OL,13,FRocio Cifuentes said: '' There may be
OL,14,Fother groups of children that for
OL,15,Fexample, children with additional
OL,16,Flearning needs or who are maybe young
OL,17,Fcarers who rely on their phones for
OL,18,Fdifferent reasons''.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
