OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781628468
OL,3,CWelsh Government sets out guidance to
OL,4,Ccurb mobile phones in schools
OL,6,F''This needs to be really carefully
OL,7,Fthought through and not brought in a
OL,8,Fkind of by a knee-jerk reaction
OL,9,Ffashion overnight''.
OL,11,FThe Association of School and College
OL,12,FLeaders says it supports the move, but
OL,13,Fadded: "it is vital to address the
OL,14,Felephant in the room which is the fact
OL,15,Fthat education funding is desperately
OL,16,Finadequate, and that schools are
OL,17,Frunning on fumes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
